Tue May  6 12:49:47 UTC 2008  Jeff Parsons <j.parsons@vanderbilt.edu>

        * orbsvcs/orbsvcs/Log/Log_Constraint_Visitors.cpp:
        * orbsvcs/orbsvcs/Log/Log_Constraint_Interpreter.cpp:
