Thu Apr 24 09:21:32 UTC 2008  Johnny Willemsen  <jwillemsen@remedy.nl>

        * tao/Adapter_Registry.{h,cpp}:
        * tao/Compression/Compression.h:
        * tao/PortableServer/Adapter_Activator.cpp:
